  rw [mem_ker]
```

Now we'll define the intersection of two ideals.

```tactics
def Ideal.inter (I J : Ideal R) : Ideal R where
  carrier := I ∩ J
  add_mem' := by
    sorry
  zero_mem' := by
    sorry
  smul_mem' := by
    sorry
```

