1. Define the map `toFun` as `kerLift f`
2. Define the map `invFun` as `fun x => (Ideal.Quotient.mk (ker f) (surjInv hf x))`
3. Prove `right_inv` as `rightInverse_surjInv hf`
4. Prove `map_mul'` (and `map_add'`, `map_one'`, `map_zero'` if needed)

We need to complete the proof of `map_mul'`.

